                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-13040&quot; title=&quot;Handle empty bucket creations more efficiently &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HIVE-13040&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HIVE-13040&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; creates 0 length ORC files. Reading such files will throw following exception. ORC is resilient to corrupt footers but not 0 length files.&lt;/p&gt;

